document_data.name: Maignith Baenre
document_data.mainbody: '''Maignith Baenre''' was a member of [[House Baenre]] circa [[1373 DR]]. She was a captain in the guard of the Baenre Compound.
document_data.History: Maignith commanded the guards during the [[Silence of Lolth]]. In 1373 DR, she died in a [[Jaezred Chaulssin]] assassination attempt on [[Matron mother]] [[Triel Baenre]].
